# Defense-in-depth: prevent a real (credential-bearing) mktxp.conf from
# being committed. The git-tracked structure lives in mktxp.conf.example;
# the runtime config is rendered by external-secret-mktxp.yaml into the
# `mktxp-credentials` Secret. Any raw mktxp.conf in this directory is by
# definition local/scratch and should not be tracked.
mktxp.conf
